Sony has announced a variety of PlayStation deals for Black Friday 2018. One of the standout offers is a Marvel Spider-Man Standard Edition PS4 Bundle, which includes a DualShock 4 wireless controller and a copy of the Spider-Man game for $200. PlayStation VR headsets are also available for $200, while DualShock 4 wireless controllers are on sale for $40. PlayStation Plus users will be offered discounts on 12-month subscriptions, and PlayStation Plus subscribers can also purchase Call of Duty: Black Ops 4 at a discounted price. Special deals on a variety of other popular games will be offered from 16-27 November. This follows Microsoft’s recently announcement of its Xbox deals, which offer the “lowest price ever” of $400 for the Xbox One X.